---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | ToolGrid" description="Read the Terms of Service for using ToolGrid.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <p class="text-muted-foreground"><strong>Last Updated: June 2026</strong></p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">By accessing and using ToolGrid, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Use License</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">Permission is granted to temporarily use the materials and tools on ToolGrid's website for personal, non-commercial, and commercial transitory viewing and processing.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">The materials on ToolGrid's website are provided on an 'as is' basis. ToolGrid makes no warranties, expressed or implied, and hereby disclaims and negates all other warranties including, without limitation, implied warranties or conditions of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement of intellectual property or other violation of rights.</p>
    
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
